Modules Factory Glad to announce the release of version 1.3 with some of the finest features and bug fixes that customers been waiting for like:

 •  **Client Area:** show ips on clientsarea, added ip to assignedips field.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Order Area:** Support VPS products build in Root Password and Hostname field.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Order Area:** Hostname custom field support for openvz.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Order Area:** Root Password custom field support for openvz.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Order Area:** OS Template Custom field for OpenVz, Customer to choose OS on Order.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Admin Area:** Support for IPv6 Pool Ranges.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Admin Area:** IP Pools new area .&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Admin Area:** Node Management new area (teaser) more to be added soon.&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **Servers:** support for non-default port for Proxmox GUI (8006).&lt;br /&gt;
 •  **KVM Template:** Arbitrary KVM arquements field in kvm Templates for experts, support for kick start scripts for auto OS install.&lt;br /&gt;

[Screenshots](https://modulesfactory.com/features.html) | [Change Log](https://modulesfactory.com/changelog.html) | [Read more and Order](https://modulesfactory.com/)


Stay tuned for next release.&lt;br /&gt;

Thanks&lt;br /&gt;
Modules Factory
